name: Perceptron
description:
Perceptron is a comic-style/anime hybrid model.

Huggingface Repo

A merge of:

  • iCoMix-V02-pruned

  • expmixLine_v20

  • Midnight Mixer Melt (as of v2.0)

  • 3moonREALPhoto_3moonREALPhotoV2 (as of v2.0)

Recommended Settings:

Sampling Method: DPM++ 2M Karras / DPM++ SDE Karras

Sampling Steps: 28-38+

Hires Fix: ✅

  • Upscaler: Latent (nearest-exact)/RealESRGAN_x4plus_anime_6B

  • Hires steps: 0

  • Denoising strength: 0.5-0.6

CFG Scale: 7.5-10

Suggested Embeddings:

  • easynegative

  • bad-hands-5

  • bad_prompt_version2

Suggested VAE:

  • anything-v4.0

  • vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned
